name: CP 17 Delay
details:
Echo DelayThe Time Space is capable of making some great slapback tones as well as some longer delays by properly manipulating the time and repeat controls. You can also create some crazy oscillation type effects when really pushing the repeat knob.
A digital pedal but still sounds very natural.
Delay Time range: 25ms ~ 600ms. 
Mix, Repeat, and Time settings. 
True Bypass design to minimize the tone loss. 
Full metal case, sturdy stomp switch. 
Can be operated with a 9-Volt Battery (NOT INCLUDED). 
Can be connected to a negative center 9-Volt power supply.
